## Gorgeous assets

### Type

All of the type is set in [Skolar](https://www.rosettatype.com/skolar "Check out Skolar on the Rosetta website"), from the amazing, award-winning [Rosetta](https://www.rosettatype.com "Check out the Rosetta website") type foundry.

Thoughout my site’s life, I’ve hosted Skolar on Typekit, Fontdeck; but as part of the static site move I converted it all over to self-hosting. I was __massively lucky__ that [David Březina](http://davi.cz/ "Check out David’s website") – the man behind Skolar – reached out and helped me subset the exact glyphs I need. We reduced the size of the fonts being served down from 750kb+ to ~150kb, whilst maintaining the opentype features that I wanted to serve!

